{"tid":2227700,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食個焗豬都會肚痾","createTime":"2020-10-03T04:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T10:51:58.000Z","uid":58851,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d749b9a6be807178f5b8743c66f855199f1896df","tid":2227700,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的.<br />\n因為當晚7點半返屋企途中, 人又覺得太攰, 所以唔想煮飯, 就去左屋企附近嘅大家樂外賣自取「一哥厚切焗豬扒飯」.<br />\n但當拎返屋企打開, 才發現裡面無左好多配料, 茄醬波羅之類個D, 但多左一堆粟米.  雖然味道變得怪怪地, 但肚餓不虞有詐, 就食左落肚.<br />\n<br />\n之後過左半個鐘就開始肚痛, 之後肚痾, 就將肚裡面D食物, 痾返晒落馬桶.<br />\n<br />\n所以希望提提大家, 下次外賣自取都係打開睇睇, 有唔妥就要換. 唔係食左肚痾就唔好啦.<br />\n再者, 快餐店員工D處理食物態度同操守都好差, 再返翻PACK呢D焗豬扒飯."},{"pid":"489c326549e1dbd2cd359f1514dfa96071f33d40","tid":2227700,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109e15f190c51b652d7b70c809f81cc4d4abe663","tid":2227700,"uid":97855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/district_offices/districtoffices/district_offices.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fdistrict_offices%2Fdistrictoffices%2Fdistrict_offices.html&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=cf037fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/district_offices/districtoffices/district_offices.html</a><br />\n<br />\n分區環境衞生辦事處開放時間、地址及聯絡號碼"},{"pid":"335ad9f70f51b110e4f82f990e62b9f21bb2d417","tid":2227700,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bac28bedba865da97f1c141590c65bfe95f6cf0","tid":2227700,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"如果你已經唔記得當初喺為咩而行出嚟，當初喺為咩而憤怒，就入嚟睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\